title: You Were Not Meant To Do This Alone (Holly Furtick)
description: God never intended for you to live out your faith in isolation. In “You Were Not Meant To Do This Alone,” Holly Furtick of Elevation Church challenges us to check our connection with Christ and the community He’s surrounded us with.
